<ex>low-cut</ex> party dress</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> decollete, low-necked.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>having a back exposing skin between the shoulder
